    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Abstract cultural concepts that influence tourism experiences in Jordan. This class enables explicit semantic reasoning about cultural requirements, constraints, and sensitivities - a key thesis innovation treating culture as first-class ontological entities.</rdfs:comment>
