    <jto:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Jordan Pass covers visa fee (for eligible nationalities) + free entry to 40+ attractions including Petra (1, 2 or 3 days). Must be purchased before arrival.</jto:description>
    <jto:sitesIncluded rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Petra, Jerash, Wadi Rum, Ajloun Castle, Umm Qais and 40+ more</jto:sitesIncluded>
