    <jto:restrictions rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Photography permitted in courtyards but NOT inside prayer halls during prayer times. Always ask permission before photographing worshippers. Remove shoes at entrance.</jto:restrictions>
